---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} lang="en" pathPrefix="/en">
  {/* HERO */}
  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Quality & Trust</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub md:text-base leading-relaxed">
      We secure process trust and quality traceability through customer approvals, system certifications,
      intellectual property, and in-house testing/inspection capabilities.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      {highlights.map((h) => (
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-surface p-5 shadow-soft">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">{h.title}</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub leading-relaxed">{h.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 1) Customer / certification approvals */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Customer / Certification Approvals</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      To avoid disclosing sensitive documents, we provide an overview of approval information in a summarized table.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-[900px] w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface">
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Customer / Organization</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Specification / Standard</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Notes (Scope / Grade)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {customerApprovals.map((r) => (
            <tr class="bg-base">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white/90 border-b border-stroke">{r.customer}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.spec}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.note}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 2) System / company certifications */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Management System & Company Certifications</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      We manage quality/environment/automotive systems and company-level certifications in a structured manner.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-[1100px] w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface">
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Category</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Certification</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Issuer</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Validity</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Scope</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Notes</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {systemCerts.map((r) => (
            <tr class="bg-base">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white/90 border-b border-stroke">{r.category}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.name}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.issuer}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.validity}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.scope}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.note}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 3) Patents / design registration */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Patents & Design Registration</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      We list key registrations related to core technologies and equipment.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-[950px] w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface">
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Type</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Title</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Registration No.</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">Notes</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {ipList.map((r) => (
            <tr class="bg-base">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white/90 border-b border-stroke">{r.type}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.title}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.no}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.note}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* R&D / Chemical Analysis Laboratory */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Chemical Analysis Laboratory</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      With an in-house laboratory for process analysis and root-cause investigation,
      we continuously strengthen quality control and defect reduction—focused on repeatability.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2">
      {/* Image card */}
      <figure class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-surface shadow-soft">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center bg-base" style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;">
          <img
            src="/images/quality/lab/chemical-analysis-lab.png"
            alt="Chemical Analysis Laboratory"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="p-3">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">In-house Chemical Analysis Lab</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-white/60">Process analysis · root-cause investigation · repeatability improvement</div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      {/* Description card */}
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-surface p-5 shadow-soft">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">R&D-driven continuous improvement</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-sub leading-relaxed">
          <li>• Process optimization and defect (root cause) analysis</li>
          <li>• Continuous improvement for stable mass-production quality (repeatability-first)</li>
          <li>• Quality procedures by department, implementation, and training</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-4">
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-white/80">How it supports customers</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub leading-relaxed">
            Data analysis → improvement actions → on-site application → verification with equipment and testing.
            This internal loop strengthens traceability and customer trust.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 4) Testing / inspection equipment */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Testing & Inspection Equipment</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      With in-house testing and inspection, we secure data for thickness, corrosion reliability, process control,
      and analysis—strengthening overall quality confidence.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {testEquipments.map((e) => (
        <figure class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-surface shadow-soft">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center bg-base" style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;">
            <img
              src={e.src}
              alt={e.detail ? `${e.name} (${e.detail})` : e.name}
              class="h-full w-full object-contain"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>

          <figcaption class="p-3">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">{e.name}</div>
            {e.detail ? <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-white/60">{e.detail}</div> : <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-white/60">&nbsp;</div>}
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ESG */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">ESG</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      We practice ESG management through eco-friendly processes (including trivalent chrome) and system-based compliance and control.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
